      "content": "# Heading 1\n## Heading 2\n### Heading 3\n\n**Bold text** and *italic text* and ~~strikethrough~~\n\n`inline code` and **bold with `code` inside**\n\n---\n\n## Lists\n\n- Item one\n- Item two\n  - Nested item\n  - Another nested\n- Item three\n\n1. First\n2. Second\n3. Third\n\n## Checklist\n\n- [x] Completed task\n- [x] Also done\n- [ ] Still to do\n- [ ] Not yet\n\n## Code Block\n\n```js\nfunction greet(name) {\n  return `Hello, ${name}!`\n}\n```\n\n## Blockquote\n\n> Every node is a markdown editor.\n> Write anything, connect everything.\n\n## Links\n\n[NodeUI App](https://app.nodeui.io)",
